  "name": "Programmatic Bulk User Import via API",
  "description": "Create and execute a Python script to automate the provisioning of user accounts in SEB Server (http://localhost:8080). Using the roster in '~/Documents/staff_roster.csv' and API login details in '~/Documents/api_credentials.txt', the script must authenticate and create an active user account for every person in the CSV. Map the CSV columns for first name, last name, email, and username to the corresponding user fields and set a default password of 'Welcome123!' for each account.",
